N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 5600.3 - Current list of records available for inspection and copying

State Regulations
A current list, by subject matter, of all records is
maintained by the secretary and shall be available for public inspection and
copying, in accordance with this Part. Notes
